com.qualcomm.snapdragon.sdk.gestures

Interface SwipeListener


  • public interface SwipeListener
    The listener interface for receiving swipe events. The class that is interested in processing a swipe event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's GestureDeviceManager.setSwipeListener(SwipeListener) method. When the swipe event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    See Also:
    SwipeListener.SwipeEvent
